    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242970/extras/d9cd298cacde0d23e01a6d481095fbb6.webp?t=1737020763\" width=601 height=52 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242970/extras/26e6e4533c33be343d98d7c5a31e34b4.poster.avif?t=1737020763\" width=600 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242970/extras/26e6e4533c33be343d98d7c5a31e34b4.webm?t=1737020763\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242970/extras/26e6e4533c33be343d98d7c5a31e34b4.mp4?t=1737020763\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Project Tower 是一款第三人称射击游戏，将激烈的子弹地狱战斗与独特的变形机制相融合。在一个受到海克威胁的宇宙中，人类的幸存者被迫在塔中作为“Project Tower”的一部分进行战斗。你扮演其中一名囚犯，目标是登顶以重获自由。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242970/extras/e75613d6fd271497bbc4c6f38a9822bc.webp?t=1737020763\" width=412 height=35 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242970/extras/da2290b99fbb6786600f20093ced1ad6.poster.avif?t=1737020763\" width=600 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242970/extras/da2290b99fbb6786600f20093ced1ad6.webm?t=1737020763\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242970/extras/da2290b99fbb6786600f20093ced1ad6.mp4?t=1737020763\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >比他们更聪明。 改变自己，更好地让敌人出其不意。 使用这种独特的机制来摆脱各种情况。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242970/extras/a23b87a48823693c0bcd17d94eefd2be.webp?t=1737020763\" width=412 height=35 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242970/extras/ef09c694b6feb8b61cd49520b5c3cdce.poster.avif?t=1737020763\" width=600 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242970/extras/ef09c694b6feb8b61cd49520b5c3cdce.webm?t=1737020763\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242970/extras/ef09c694b6feb8b61cd49520b5c3cdce.mp4?t=1737020763\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款射击游戏中，参与一场调动你所有感官的激烈战斗。 使用新武器调整你的游戏风格。 从一层楼上升到另一层楼。 磨练你的技能以达到顶峰。 重拾自由的滋味。 不惜一切代价，攀登。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242970/extras/e0a6c4ebfce27e6e2e484caf976a872e.webp?t=1737020763\" width=412 height=35 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242970/extras/e919ffc098b37a293fc849f31b36fe1b.poster.avif?t=1737020763\" width=600 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242970/extras/e919ffc098b37a293fc849f31b36fe1b.webm?t=1737020763\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242970/extras/e919ffc098b37a293fc849f31b36fe1b.mp4?t=1737020763\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索塔的不同楼层，面对成群的可怕敌人，解决复杂的谜题，并使用你的武器库解开塔的秘密并重获自由。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >参与冒险。 让自己沉浸在这个新宇宙中。 你准备好接受塔楼的挑战了吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款激动人心的第三人射击游戏。 玩一款既充满活力又令人满意的游戏。 游戏感觉是首要任务。 提高你的感官来战胜你的敌人。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >创新的变形机制，可以增加游戏玩法的可能性。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个丰富的宇宙。 发现这座塔的秘密并重获自由！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁新武器和技能。 驯服外星技术来实现你的目标。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >连续镜头过场动画，带来完美的沉浸感。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242970/extras/4e82cdea461a5dfef09eededa89174e9.poster.avif?t=1737020763\" width=600 height=50 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242970/extras/4e82cdea461a5dfef09eededa89174e9.webm?t=1737020763\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242970/extras/4e82cdea461a5dfef09eededa89174e9.mp4?t=1737020763\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
